Title: Alone
Plot: With his diagnostic team gone, House tries to diagnose a young woman who survived an office building collapse. With the condition getting worse, Cuddy puts pressure on House to hire a new team, but instead attempts a differential diagnosis with help from the janitor.
GuestStars: Liliya Toneva, Kay Lenz, Conor Dubin, Bevin Prince, Pat Millicano, Kathryn Adams, Ken Takemoto, Leo Vargas, Maurice Godin, Xhercis, Shannon McClung
